PART: Recipes
NAME: Recipes
STATUS: draft

DATA: Recipe List
MARKER: recipe_list
INTENT: holds all recipes and their details
LOCK: approved
---
The app holds a list of recipes. Each recipe has a title, a preparation time, a difficulty level, and a list of ingredients.

STRUCTURE: Recipe Screen
MARKER: recipe_screen
INTENT: the main screen showing all recipes
LOCK: locked
---
The screen has a top bar with the app name, a scrollable list of recipe cards, and a floating add button in the bottom right.

WHEN: Add Recipe
MARKER: add_recipe
INTENT: user adds a new recipe
LOCK: approved
---
When the user taps the add button, a form appears. The user fills in the recipe title, preparation time, difficulty level, and ingredients. The new recipe appears at the top of the list.

WHEN: Mark Recipe as Favorite
MARKER: mark_favorite
INTENT: user marks a recipe as a favorite
---
When the user taps the star icon on a recipe card, the recipe status changes to favorite. The star icon turns gold, and the recipe moves to the top of the list.

ASSERT: Recipe Title Validation
MARKER: recipe_title_validation
INTENT: ensure recipe titles are not empty
---
A recipe title cannot be empty.

SURFACE: Recipe Card
MARKER: recipe_card
INTENT: labels and text for recipe cards
---
The recipe card displays the recipe title, preparation time, and a list of ingredients. The star icon is labeled "Favorite".
---PART---

PART: Tasks
NAME: Tasks
STATUS: draft

DATA: Task List
MARKER: task_list
INTENT: holds all tasks and their state
---
The app holds a list of tasks. Each task has a title, a completion status, and a creation date.

STRUCTURE: Task Screen
MARKER: task_screen
INTENT: the main screen showing all tasks
LOCK: approved
---
The screen has a top bar with the app name, a scrollable list of task cards, and a floating add button in the bottom right.

WHEN: Complete Task
MARKER: complete_task
INTENT: user marks a task as done
LOCK: approved
---
When the user taps the checkbox on a task card, the task status changes to complete. The card moves to the bottom of the list with a strikethrough style.

ASSERT: Task Title Validation
MARKER: task_title_validation
INTENT: ensure task titles are not empty
---
A task title cannot be empty.